name: #32. “Doodles” the Gogo
description:
Claims to be from another planet. Could possibly be true. 

“What’s a bunny’s favourite music?”
“What do you call a rabbit comedian?”
“What is orange and sounds like a parrot?”
“How can you say rabbit without using the letter R?”


'r' toggles auto-rotate. 
‘l’ toggles look around.

Artist: Arya Mularama (https://twitter.com/gogoporen)
